Sentencas: La0.5Sr0.5CoO3 - delta and La0.6Sr0.4CoO3 - delta are characterized with respect to application as cathode materials in intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Comparison of oxygen exchange kinetics of the IT-SOFC cathode materials La0.5Sr0.5CoO3 - δ and La0.6Sr0.4CoO3 - δ

Sentencas: Surface exchange and transport parameters of oxygen are determined by the conductivity relaxation technique between 525 degrees C and 725 degrees C at oxygen partial pressures of 0.1, 0.01 and 0.001 bar.
Titulo: Comparison of oxygen exchange kinetics of the IT-SOFC cathode materials La0.5Sr0.5CoO3 - δ and La0.6Sr0.4CoO3 - δ

Sentencas: Electrical conductivities of both compounds range between 1000 and 2400 S cm(-1) and are slightly higher for La0.6Sr0.4CoO3 - delta.
Titulo: Comparison of oxygen exchange kinetics of the IT-SOFC cathode materials La0.5Sr0.5CoO3 - δ and La0.6Sr0.4CoO3 - δ

Sentencas: However, La0.5Sr0.5CoO3 - delta shows superior performance with regard to oxygen diffusion, ionic conductivity and oxygen surface exchange within the investigated range of temperatures and oxygen partial pressures.
Titulo: Comparison of oxygen exchange kinetics of the IT-SOFC cathode materials La0.5Sr0.5CoO3 - δ and La0.6Sr0.4CoO3 - δ

Sentencas: At 725 degrees C the chemical surface exchange coefficient of oxygen is 2 x 10(-3) cm s(-1) for La0.5Sr0.5CoO3 - delta and 4 x 10(-4) cm s(-1) for La0.6Sr0.4CoO3 - delta.
Titulo: Comparison of oxygen exchange kinetics of the IT-SOFC cathode materials La0.5Sr0.5CoO3 - δ and La0.6Sr0.4CoO3 - δ

Sentencas: At lower oxygen partial pressures a strong decrease in the surface exchange coefficient is observed and diffusion data cannot be obtained from relaxation measurements.
Titulo: Comparison of oxygen exchange kinetics of the IT-SOFC cathode materials La0.5Sr0.5CoO3 - δ and La0.6Sr0.4CoO3 - δ

Sentencas: Oxygen vacancy diffusion coefficients are similar for both compounds and range between 10(-6) and 10(-8)
Titulo: Comparison of oxygen exchange kinetics of the IT-SOFC cathode materials La0.5Sr0.5CoO3 - δ and La0.6Sr0.4CoO3 - δ
